name: Tulalip Tribes of Washington Quil Ceda Creek Counseling

narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Tulalip Tribes of Washington Quil Ceda Creek Counseling is a Clinic/Center  Methadone Clinic provider based in Tulalip, WA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $22.3M in Medicaid payments across 73K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $22.3M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
